headline: Show HN: Boilerplate Generator Node.js, Express, TypeScript/JavaScript Projects
description:
Hello there, I've built a simple, lightweight boilerplate generator for node.js, express typescript/javascript apps. Here's the Github repo: https://github.com/gunvantsr/expressgen

I would appreciate any feedback or suggestions. thank, you!
